---
By: David Grayson
Locus:
  Page: 301
  Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Little
---
Blessed is the man who can enjoy the small things, the common beauties, the
little day-by-day events; sunshine on the fields, birds on the bough,
breakfast, dinner, supper, the daily paper on the porch, a friend passing
by. So many people who go afield for enjoyment leave it behind them at
home.
